        "summary": "Regarding \"Curriculum Cohesion and Pacing\" under \"Professional Practice\", students highlighted that while the basic concepts are generally understood, there is a clear opportunity to improve the practical guidance and clarity of instructions. A consistent framework would reduce anxiety and help students align their expectations with the staff.",
