      "no comments",
      "I wish it had been clearer from the beginning what the possibilities within de docent are for counselling/guidance. It wasn't clear to me, which caused me to struggle throughout the significant amount of time of my study, until I found the right faculty for that (and even then, it happened only after bouncing off so many people and a lack of clear information). I think if the information about it was clearer, also to the teachers who are the first contact for us students, they could have informed us better too.",
      "Je moet ervoor zorgen dat je de volgende keer geen studenten voor gaat trekken",
