          "Nee ik heb geen toevoegingen",
          "I really started to care and love about the things I am doing in de campus especially when I changed from de omstandigheden semester to a de omstandigheden. But what happened to me since I started the semester I had some issues last year, I was not in de campus in month September and I joined the semester late… 3 weeks late!! So groups were made and everyone had known each other and when I arrived I didn’t like the environment of my group, I didn’t feel welcome however I tried my best to be able to engage with them I brought chocolates, cake and juices twice and I had to listen to them and do everything they asked,  but everytime I worked on something related to group work the amount of negativity is insane:  (1.”Usage of AI is too much” 2. My contents doesn’t make any sense!! 3. “It’s not what we are looking for” 4. Did you read what we wrote?)   I felt pressure and anxiety especially when I had to work on my group project parts, thousands of questions has been asked and gossiped! But for them? They supported each others and when one of them came late or absent it was alright “forgiven father” but me coming late or being absent because I am sick? Getting gossiped and started arguments with me on WhatsApp when they all supported each others and one day they decided to take me to the teacher and exam board to question me but I refused because I felt like a prisoner!! And when this pressure and stress elevated I have decided to leave the group and start working on my own but unfortunately my room got robbed on the weekend(laptop, monitor even my clothes were stolen!!) So I had to leave the semester and start again in February 2026 HOPEFULLY!",
